 via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aChristian lifevEarly works to 1800. 0aEmblems. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh1 aSchilling, Michael, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Literary and Cultural Studies - 1990 - 1999z9783110637830oZDB-23-GLC0 cprintz978348417704840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311094052740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110940527423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110940527/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GLCc1990d1999